      "body" : "This is the ideal solution for Gradle 6.0+ since this will also create the appropriate variants with the proper capabilities and attach them to the &quot;java&quot; component for publication. If you have additional components or variants then you can also call the internal helper function manually: <code>JvmPluginsHelper.configureDocumentationVariantWithAritfact(m&zwnj;&#8203;ySourceSet.sourcesEl&zwnj;&#8203;ementsConfigurationN&zwnj;&#8203;ame, mySourceSet.name, DocsTypes.SOURCES, listOf(), mySourceSet.sourcesJarTaskName, mySourceSet.allSource, mySourceSetComponent, configurations, tasks, serviceOf()</code>."
